Gg_Timber_Bridge

Made by The Giblets of Jesus

___________________________________ This map originally started out as a 24 hour challenge I set myself to get back into mapping. Work started 14:47 on Friday and finally ended 00:07 the following day :P. Obviously not solid work, but it was pretty taxing to say the least. The next few days, I set about making tweaks testing and such so actually the total time spent on this is somewhere around the 10 - 20 hour mark. If you do spot any bugs or have any suggestions to make, don't hesitate to leave a comment and I'll get onto fixing it as soon as I can :) ___________________________________

A few Features of this map:

+Constant, high FPS
+HDR
+56 Spawns
+Waterfall :D
+Isometric layout.
+Large open design with multiple routes to each spawn, ideal for large amounts of players :).
